         openssl,
         systemd (>= 235),
Conflicts: ${ws:Conflicts}
Suggests: sssd-dbus
Description: Cockpit Web Service
 The Cockpit Web Service listens on the network, and authenticates
 users.
 .
 Install sssd-dbus for supporting client certificate/smart card authentication
 via sssd/FreeIPA.

